    <bug_when>2014-04-09 16:45:14 -0700</bug_when>
    <thetext>Requirement could go something among the lines of:

&gt; The result of `RegExp.prototype.toString`, when called on a regular expression object, should be usable as a regular expression literal.</thetext>
